rcial</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"fce61d55-92ed-4dca-a2a6-29fb90d2557d\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"0cf87f08-cadc-4646-83a5-749b7c38114e\">Expiración de Solicitud de Pago (horas)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"a4bfae12-3af7-4be1-960f-9828b4252f1a\">0.25</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"87ed7ee5-1a1d-45b0-92d9-7d7737e62cf8\">Validez del Token de Pago (años)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"68cffead-dea0-4e6c-8b72-99eca92d9b5e\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"ba0dce38-3f3e-49d7-ae0d-da0beca04eb7\">Tiempo de Liquidación (horas)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"14e766a1-2c6e-480a-8f6b-6a62bb6258bf\">T+2 BUSINESS DAYS</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"94784d78-3f48-4267-bcfa-f5baf2381b19\">Reembolso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"323aad3c-8115-450e-9e69-5ddb6843d696\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"463\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3